msg":"雲加是咪同佢反左面？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"兩父子邊有隔夜仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40820834bee76604d9f51bbe9de5579bce30a69","tid":2439313,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b95cf9af18c73e2fd4890392556bdd074014e1c","tid":2439313,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e5211461f27fb4c09cc4b634476c337a915690f","tid":2439313,"uid":9710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"雲加垂簾聽政ok?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"雲加是咪同佢反左面？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"成為教練之後，真的讓我開了眼界。我更加理解雲加了，也更加理解自己當年踢球時一起合作過的教練們了。教練這份工作並不容易，特別是所有人都能在媒體評論你，認為他們比教練本人更了解球隊。教練這份工作非常複雜，非常困難。最高水平的教練必須處理好他同媒體、戰術、贊助商、球會財政狀況，以及所有人的關係，還要知道如何堅持自己。"},{"pid":"04004329eb5dfb48f6c9a6c9d5e19522395beebc","tid":2439313,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"可以做前鋒教練，教比比 拿卡果堆撚樣埋門。"},{"pid":"997a13c4c3fc3feffee3679396391fa1358852eb","tid":2439313,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04004329eb5dfb48f6c9a6c9d5e19522395beebc","tid":2439313,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"可以做前鋒教練，教比比 拿卡果堆撚樣埋門。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"班撚樣埋門仲廢過你 拖出去打靶好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7150da623bcbaa43dbfbf103cb7895564c7a86","tid":2439313,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"997a13c4c3fc3feffee3679396391fa1358852eb","tid":2439313,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04004329eb5dfb48f6c9a6c9d5e19522395beebc","tid":2439313,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"可以做前鋒教練，教比比 拿卡果堆撚樣埋門。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"班撚樣埋門仲廢過你 拖出去打靶好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/n